Accessing Small LeftBrace AllSmallLeftBrace is an accessor function for accessing the complete list of non-isomorphic leftbrace models from orders 2 to 3.
The models are generated by Mace4 , using the definitions in Section .

Definition of LeftBrace formulas(LeftBrace).
(x*(y+z)) + x = (x*y)+(x*z).
